# [[golden rule]]; [[reciprocity]]
#: {{zh-x|子貢 問 曰：「有 一 言 而 可 以 終身 行 之 者 乎？」子.曰：「其 恕 乎！己 所 不 欲，勿 施 於 人。」|Zi Gong asked, saying, "Is there one word which may serve as a rule of practice for all one's life?" The Master said, "Is not '''RECIPROCITY''' such a word? What you do not want done to yourself, do not do to others."|ref=Analects||collapsed=y|CL}}
